@prefix this: <https://w3id.org/np/RAfW-3r_CfDhElo8eASjkuTnanXG8oUEqIkffYKwu9LAY> .
@prefix sub: <https://w3id.org/np/RAfW-3r_CfDhElo8eASjkuTnanXG8oUEqIkffYKwu9LAY/> .
@prefix biochementity: <https://w3id.org/peh/biochementities/> .
@prefix dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
